Type: Package
Package: koel
Title: Email Alerts Based on Records from a Biodiversity Data Resource
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Martin", "Westgate", email = "martin.westgate@csiro.au", role = "aut"),
    person("Callum", "Waite", email = "callum.waite@csiro.au", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Shandiya", "Balasubramaniam", email = "shandiya.balasubramaniam@csiro.au", role = "aut"))       
Description: A workflow that facilitates the process of searching for taxa 
    within spatial and temporal constraints, creating a summary table of this 
    information, converting the table into html format, and embedding the html
    file in an email. 
